@startuml
title Secure MFA Healthcare Access Portal - UML Class Diagram

class User {
  +user_id: int
  +username: string
  +password_hash: string
  +role_id: int
}

class Role {
  +role_id: int
  +role_name: string
}

class MFAChallenge {
  +challenge_id: int
  +user_id: int
  +code: string
  +expires_at: datetime
  +verified: bool
}

class AuditLog {
  +log_id: int
  +user_id: int
  +action: string
  +timestamp: datetime
}

class ProtectedRecord {
  +record_id: int
  +owner_id: int
  +masked_data: string
  +tokenized_value: string
}

class RouteHandler {
  +handleRequest()
}

class Controller {
  +login()
  +verifyMFA()
  +viewRecord()
}

class AuthService {
  +authenticateUser()
  +generateMFA()
  +verifyMFA()
}

class SecurityHelper {
  +hashPassword()
  +checkAccess()
  +maskData()
  +tokenizeData()
}

class Repository {
  +getUser()
  +saveAuditLog()
  +getProtectedRecord()
}

RouteHandler --> Controller : Handles Requests
Controller --> AuthService : Calls
Controller --> Repository : Accesses
AuthService --> SecurityHelper : Uses
AuthService --> User : Authenticates
AuthService --> MFAChallenge : Generates and Verifies
Repository --> User : Retrieves
Repository --> Role : Retrieves
Repository --> AuditLog : Stores 
Repository --> ProtectedRecord : Retrieves

User --> Role : Assigned Role
User --> MFAChallenge : Initiates MFA
User --> AuditLog : Generates Log 
User --> ProtectedRecord : Owns 

@enduml